cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with local descriptor learning, which is a common problem in computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new loss function that relies on deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on different datasets, which could make it relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
